    "description": {
      "value": "<em>You can do more with your blade than slash and stab.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Exotic Weapon Proficiency (Aldori dueling sword), Weapon Finesse, base attack bonus +2.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>Choose one of the following combat maneuvers: disarm, reposition, steal, sunder, or trip. You gain a +2 bonus when performing the selected maneuver while wielding an Aldori dueling sword. This bonus does not stack with the bonus provided by a combat maneuver feat with 'improved' in its name (such as Improved Trip).<br/><br/><b>Special</b><br/>You can select this feat multiple times, choosing a different combat maneuver each time.",
